data.name: txtInstructions.Text
data.value:
Below are some important instructions to be followed while importing data from Excel files.
For sales data import: 1. File format should be "xlsx". "xls" format is not supported. 2. There shall be only one sheet per file.
For purchase data import: 1. File format should be "xlsx". "xls" format is not supported. 2. There shall be only one sheet per file 3. Sheet headers should be as shown in graphic below.
For product list import: 1. Make sure that the target file (from where to import) is having only ONE sheet.
